 "html": "<p>Sometimes you read something on the internet and then you decide that's what I want to make.  That was the case with the little apple tarts.  Lochner de Kock showed it to me on YouTube.  I initially thought it was difficult.  Believe me it is so easy.  It looks gorgeous and tastes even better.  <a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-029.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2299\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-029-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 029\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>1 Apple.  Core removed and cut into thin slices.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-009.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2288\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-009-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 009\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>Put the slices in a bowl with water and the juice of one lemon.  Microwave on high for 3 minutes.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2289\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-010-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 010\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In another little bowl melt 2 teaspoons apricot jam with 1 teaspoon water in the microwave for 1 minute.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-012.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2290\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-012-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 012\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>Buy puff pastry and cut it into strips of about 10 cm.  Spread with the apricot jam.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2292\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-018-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 018\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Arrange the apple slices on top and let them overlap. They must stick out above the edge of the pastry.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2293\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-019-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 019\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Sprinkle cinnamon powder over the apples.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-020.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2294\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-020-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 020\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Fold the pastry up from underneath over the apples. Start at one end and roll it up carefully.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-022.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2296\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-022-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 022\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Place it in a muffin pan that has been well sprayed with Spray and Cook.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2298\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-023-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 023\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Bake it for 35 minutes at 180 degrees.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-040.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2303\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-040-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 040\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Take it out and eat it cold or warm.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-035.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2300\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-035-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 035\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Especially delicious and pretty.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-039.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2302\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/appeltertjies-039-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"appeltertjies 039\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
 "recipe": null
}
